invalid type: string "Modification No. 1 accepts assignment of the Employee Leasing Agreement from GovTempsUSA, LLC to MGT of America Consulting, LLC effective December 8, 2023. The rate is set at $53.20 per hour for an Outsourced Grant Specialist position with a total cap of $373,250 from October 23, 2023 through October 23, 2024, funded entirely by ARPA dollars for federal grant compliance work.